QUALITY
We always deliver the highest quality of service and top-notch projects. By achieving superior solutions, Northprim ensures long-lasting relations with our partners.

INNOVATION
We always strive to do things better and more efficiently by challenging the status quo; we believe that products and services can always be improved.

FLEXIBILITY
We quickly adapt to new conditions through working with novel industries, and we gladly expand our expertise to encompass new and innovative purposes.

TEAMWORK
We know that collaborative problem-solving leads to better results, so we always work towards achieving joint goals together.

WORK-LIFE BALANCE
By maintaining a healthy work-life balance we reduce stress in the collective and ensure a quality experience in everything we do.

TRUST & INTEGRITY
It is our motto and creed to treat our clients with integrity and live up to our reputation of a trusted partner that appreciates our clients’ assets and know-how.

e5ce9484-ffc2-4c02-9f38-4ded4651c269.text:
DIB Travel
DIB Travel is a prize awarded platform for corporate travel that is disrupting the corporate travel industry. DIB travel e-commerce platform is a custom built SaaS platform that enables content with its powerful integrations towards Expedia and Booking.com, as well as E2E financial flow.
ABOUT
Northprim happily helped DIB Travel with:

Setting up the IT – Tech organisation and Ways of Working
Scaling the Tech team with 35 people during course of 1 year
Development of new functionalities and maintaining existing ones
 
SaaS management and billing engine
Single Sign on – SSO and SCIM User Provisioning
Order and Checkout
Payment with Stripe and VCC
ERP integration MS Dynamics 
Analytics and reporting
API development (REST)
Investigation and implementation of QA strategies and tools
Produced Infrastructure cloud provider migration plan
Security and data privacy assessment and support for ISO-certifications
Tech Stacks used: Java, Spring Boot, MySQL, MongoDB, Maven

81008a17-ad87-4ebf-a93a-f1ad6faa8a4e.text:
Wisentic
Wisentic offers configurable online services to the insurance industry, with the goal to provide the end customers an easier insurance handling process, reducing the administration with the insurance companies. Wisentic is operating in Sweden and Norway and handles more than 250000 claims/applications yearly.
ABOUT
Wisentic, with a long company tradition, started off digitalising their business many years ago, once again sat down and outlined the vision for the future, assuring they would meet and exceed the needs of the business landscape of tomorrow.
One such big technological leap was to migrate the older system (based on PHP) to a more versatile .NET CORE and Angular based solution, that would enable Wisentic to migrate to a microservice based architecture deployed on Azure cloud. This shift is an instrumental enabler for Wisentic to continue to introduce new products and services at a rapid pace.
Northprim is a long term trusted partner, with a dedicated team since 2019, is working side by side with excellent Wisentic Solution Architects and Product Owners, sprint after sprint, month after month, year after year – always there to support Wisentic and their clients.
Northprim is delivering it’s development services from Belgrade and the results include:
Development of new products (new business areas)
Migration of legacy code to a modern microservice architecture based on .NET core, Angular and Azure frameworks using the Controller/Business/Repository pattern
Migration to Azure Cloud, implementing infrastructure as a code 
Setup of deployment pipelines for automatic deployment
Swagger setup 
Upgrading the Wicentic Mobile app to the latest version of the Ionic Framework

edde2e58-51ac-4c08-9b92-4c7cbf3b1f9f.text:
Northprim is an international tech collective, founded in Sweden in 2015. Our motto has always been collaboration and precisely this approach has unlocked continuous creative excellence in our team and helped us build exceptionally great products over the years.
Tech itself runs through our veins at Northprim, cruising down all departments, including dev, data, and analytics. We have proudly gained the trust and confidence from a large number of clients over the years and we continue to do our part for a stronger and sleeker tech society.
